About:
------

MLAPD is a Mailing List access manager which works as a Policy Access deamon for Postfix and uses LDAP to check for user's rights to post messages. You can find further details on the deployment practices at https://github.com/gfidente/mlapd


Requirements:
------------

* Python ( >= 2.4 )
* Python-LDAP ( >= 2.2.0 )

Postfix and your LDAP daemon can be installed on a remote machine.


Support:
--------

Please use the mailing list at: http://groups.google.com/group/mlapd


Reporting bugs:
---------------

You can check for known bugs or submit new ones at: https://github.com/gfidente/mlapd/issues
